				"code" : "\"1. Locate the file in your home directory\"\rfileName := 'credentials'.\rfileReference := FileLocator home / '.veracode' / fileName.\r\"2. Read the file contents (handles opening and closing automatically)\"\nfileContents := fileReference readStreamDo: [ :stream | stream contents ].\r\"3. Example of parsing: split by newlines, then by commas\"\nparsedData := fileContents lines collect: [ :line | \n    line findTokens: ',' \n]."
			},
